txt.en: An Ikorbâni scout has arrived to escort you back to Urmâkh
Find and defeat Tamâhu, the dread-scorpion.
Tamâhu snaps his pincers in warning at your approach
Scorpions near Dûlagig have been expanding their reach and are growing more aggressive in their attacks. Cull their number before they become an even great threat to Urmâkh.
'These scorpions make my skin crawl. I'm glad you were able to thin their number. Let's get back to Urmâkh to report the good news!'
Defeat scorpions and destroy their burrows to cull their number.
